metadata.description: Figure 1 Phylogram of Entoloma subg. Cyanula spp. generated by Bayesian inference (BI) analysis based on ITS and LSU, rooted with E. subgenus Nolanea spp. Bayesian inference (BI-PP) ≥ 0.95 and ML bootstrap proportions (ML-BP) ≥ 95% are indicated as PP/BP. The new taxa are marked in bold.
